snippet.title: ElderFox Documentaries
snippet.description:
Here, you can learn, be entertained and find comfort. It's our mission to make interesting, thought provoking and fun videos about Space, Science and History. A new video every Saturday!

We are on the road to 1 Million subscribers, join the team now by subscribing!
https://www.youtube.com/channel/UCZvxw99l3xDC6BIHb8nJKGg?sub_confirmation=1

Why should I subscribe? 
If you are interested at all in the type of videos we make, then by subscribing you help to get more of these videos on YouTube. There is a direct correlation between the amount of subscribers we have, and the amount of videos we can post. Each and every one of you that decides to subscribe makes a difference. Join the team today!

Feel free to send video suggestions/ask questions at elderfoxdocumentaries@gmail.com

Please note: We are not affiliated with NASA in any way, we just want more people to be inspired by their great work.
